{"tid":1168101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"EDM撚同非EDM撚都入一入黎","createTime":"2019-05-23T12:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T10:48:31.000Z","uid":254961,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"096a895313614bbd94dad8d7cc711cd42337bf97","tid":1168101,"uid":254961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"between講之前睇一睇呢段<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民陣6.9反惡法遊行  日期：6月9日（日） <br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道 時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道立法會</span><br />\n<br />\n借一借個台黎發表下心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能負皮仲多過唯唯(梁烈唯)有獎拎呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知好多人唔知咩係<span style=\"color: red;\">電子音樂</span> ，就算連日日去蒲既人都未必識<br />\n其實未接觸過既人會覺得好嘈，唔知做乜鳩,呢個真，我以前都係咁諗<br />\n，但請你聽我廢up幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次都係比個老死推薦我， 叫我聽下，開頭我都嫌棄呢d歌「好撚嘈」<br />\n但後尾慢慢聽下聽下又會跟住個beat，好似好治癒咁，於是我就上網搵啦<br />\n咁岩比我見到有位台灣既Youtuber : I.C Charlie<br />\n有條片寫住 【DJ介紹】，丫，又幾撚得意喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q4rWWyNUB9g&amp;t=1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ4rWWyNUB9g%26t%3D1s&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b278b484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q4rWWyNUB9g&amp;t=1s</a><br />\n<br />\n原來當你了解到呢個<span style=\"color: red;\">EDM(電子音樂)</span>文化背景，製作過程，生態圈之後<br />\n發現電子音樂原來仲有細分好多唔同種類：<span style=\"color: green;\">#electrohouse</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">#progressivehouse</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">#dubstep</span><span style=\"color: brown;\"> #techno</span>#<span style=\"color: violet;\">trance</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">#trap </span>　以上都係大部份主流既種類<br />\n其實係會用一種Respect既心態去聽<br />\n樓豬我本身係一位90後,細個成日同班fd去玩，玩到殘哂<br />\n大個左出黎做野做左幾年，慢慢同班朋友見既次數越黎越小，公司又清一色麻甩佬<br />\n後來個人變得好毒，鐘意留係屋企煮下飯，自己去做下運動<br />\n依加同女友同居 ，所以想去玩或者識人之類更加唔洗講<br />\n所以唯有做一個毒撚鍵盤戰士去宣揚呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n如果想嘗試聽電子音樂既巴絲打 <br />\n建議你地去youtube搵tomorrowland(明日世界電子音樂節)其實中文好撚畢<br />\ntomorrowland係一個超大型國際型既電子音樂節，<br />\n2011年，音樂節從兩天擴大到三天的規模，短短的幾天內票就銷售一空，吸引了共18萬人前往。<br />\n2014人數也再次達到顛峰，兩個禮拜共36萬人參與這場盛會。<br />\n見到一大班人咁有共嗚,真係好希望身邊果班朋友就係片入面果堆人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xg7sptEx0Ms&amp;t=904s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxg7sptEx0Ms%26t%3D904s&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=a37a5737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xg7sptEx0Ms&amp;t=904s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提<br />\n香港都會有大型電子音樂節，如果有興趣既真係可以去感受下<br />\ne.g Roadtoultra (超世代音樂節)簡稱ultra  / creamfields  (奶油田) 都係香港舉辦過<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n我好希望可以將呢樣野宣揚開去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我搞呢個Pages無收過任何人一分一毫 任何利益 etc club event 邀請</span> <br />\n只係純粹希望想身邊既人都知道呢一類音樂 都係好正能量 好舒服 好撚爽<br />\nbetween唔好吸毒 唔好濫藥　唔洗食呢D都可以開心既係咪 <br />\n<br />\nIG&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong.edm.official/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong.edm.official%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=383916ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong.edm.official/?hl=zh-hk</a><br />\n Facebook&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkedmofficial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkedmofficial%2F&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=3c5f0a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkedmofficial/</a><br />\nWhatsapp谷&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://chat.whatsapp.com/GullYN0CFUv1tU8iNNw4v3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchat.whatsapp.com%2FGullYN0CFUv1tU8iNNw4v3&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b562a11d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chat.whatsapp.com/GullYN0CFUv1tU8iNNw4v3</a>"},{"pid":"1447a5efea5097c5c88bf52b8f737f73ca1156b3","tid":1168101,"uid":23468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"EDM係垃圾嚟，即食音樂加幾句口水<br />\n真。電音迷只有tech house/techno"},{"pid":"ef5b00a48b37f0087d51809ca07e66f6d71970bb","tid":1168101,"uid":245676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1447a5efea5097c5c88bf52b8f737f73ca1156b3","tid":1168101,"uid":23468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"EDM係垃圾嚟，即食音樂加幾句口水<br />\n真。電音迷只有tech house/techno"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐你 EDM得個響"},{"pid":"8fd4ffa7f2ab2f511f5995a052b313a66d68fde1","tid":1168101,"uid":68183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"識玩EDM FESTIVAL 一定係出國玩，香港果啲垃撚垃，個個mk 仔當落club 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4a415b823039c9d3a25962a1cef96c05beea0e","tid":1168101,"uid":68183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fd4ffa7f2ab2f511f5995a052b313a66d68fde1","tid":1168101,"uid":68183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"識玩EDM FESTIVAL 一定係出國玩，香港果啲垃撚垃，個個mk 仔當落club 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"83e14e8f02cfd6506bf779683282adacfe39a75a","tid":1168101,"uid":206024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc